Dialogs.Dialog: Is it stretched under your nose?
Geez, don't look so much okay?
Hey, it's a little too much... isn't it?
If you have any questions, please ask okay?
I feel like I can sleep slowly tonight...
I want to stop the time...
Your hands are gentle... like you?
Would you like to go somewhere else? I'm kidding.
……Yes. Just a little more, like this...
I wonder what should I do. I don't want to leave...
I still want to do this...
I don't want to let go...
Let's stay like this a little more, okay?
This kind of thing may not be bad.
I'm feeling this for the first time...
I'm glad to be with you.
Fufu~, I love you... I'm kidding。
It's fun... I'm letting you know.
I wonder what causes you to laugh.
I wonder if this is fun.
Wouldn't it be nice to have this kind of time?
I want to sing something. Fufu.
Do you know what you're doing? ...Geez.
...It's your fault that my face is red.
I want to do this forever...
Fufu, stay with me like this okay?
You hate it, right? That sort of thing.
Can you think a little more?
I'm so happy. It's a little scary.
To other people... it's no good?
Look at me right, okay? Only me.
Fufu~, I love you... I'm kidding。
Fufu... It's a bit embarrassing, isn't it?
I'm doing my best to care for my hair.
When you pet me, I feel sleepy.
Your sleeping habits shouldn't been like that...
Fufu, are you trying to generate static electricity?
Please fix it later. I'm kidding。
Be a little more gentle, please?
I feel like a dog or a cat.
I don't think I have a fever...
How are you? It's that bad?
Only when you touch, it seems to get hot.
That's about it, I'm not surprised.
What is it? A naughty story?
That's forbidden because I will lose my strenght.
Hmm~! Geez, that's a pear. Right?
Fufu~, would you lean on me?
Yes, I wonder what should I do.
Isn't this useless on someone else?
If we hold hands, you'll feel relieved...
Do you want to connect with your lover? I'm kidding.
I can't hear the sound of the heart...
I'll be aware when I come to such a place...
...What are you planning to do coming so close?
Isn't it a bit far? I'm kidding...
Even if we get closer. I'm fine...
Is this distance my only privilege?
I don't mind doing what you want...
One more time... It's no good...
What are you going to do with me?
I'm happy... Are you happy too?
Are you in good shape? I'm kidding.
Y-you know, my heart isn't ready yet...
...Fufu, what are you trying to do?
What do you want to do? Geez...
I wonder if I did something to bother you...
It's a bit far, I'm kidding...
Is it okay to go near...?
You can reduce the distance, right?
I want to feel you more...
I don't want to leave even one milimeter...
I want to feel you more...?
...Shall we do it a little more?
Just a little more, it's good isn't it?
I don't like this to end...
Hey, one more time... is it okay?
Would you like to try again...?
You wouldn't tell me to stop...?
I wonder what should I do...
I want to know more about you...
I want to touch you more...
I want to stay this way, forever...
It looks like there's not enough...
...I'm waiting for it, okay? My kiss.
Kiss... I don't want to, I'm kidding...
I will give out my courage...
I have to do it quickly...
Maybe I should call you sensei...
You can't solve such a problem...
I have to punish a bad boy who's forgotten his homework...
Can't you hear what the sensei says?
Such a short skirt... If you were my Master...
Welcome home, Master. Do you want to eat? I'm kidding...
After you eat, there is a delicious dessert, Master...
I have to give my Master a massage before going to bed...
Give me a dessert after eating...
If you eat this much, you'll gain weight... but...
Beign late... it's no good... Umm.
Club activities... I have to my best...
Preparation/review, I have to do it properly...
I wish I could see that much...
Ya~... Yes, it doesn't mean I don't.
Hey~, what do you want to do?
Emm... no one is watching, right?
Yes. I want you to come.
It's not funny, even for a girl...
I want you to spoil me.
I want a wake up kiss, I'm kidding... Fufu.
I dont want to get out of the futon~...
Even in a dream, I could meet you... Fufu.
Ah, is that? ...Ah, it's my home...
